docs/20260402-cypherclaw-embodiment-prd.md:207:- Lifecycle: Characters appear → persist briefly → dissolve/fade/morph into the surrounding GlyphWeave glyphs
docs/20260402-cypherclaw-embodiment-prd.md:219:- Registered as "The Scribe" sensory voice
